quran[44]{c,v,t}:
  23,75,"Xas Nêun fellasen, u Nekkes asen ccqa nnsen, ad vellelen di leqheô nnsen, ad ddebdeben"
  23,76,"Ni$ Nesâadda fellasen aâaqeb. Ur knan i Mass nnsen, ur nujen"
  23,77,"Armi, mara asen Nelli tabburt uâaqeb iqesêen, imiren, degs, ad aysen"
  23,78,"Neppa i wen Ixelqen timesliwt, iéôi, ulawen. Drus ay tesnemmirem"
  23,79,Neppa ikwen Iwezzâen di tmurt. £uôeS ara tepwafesrem
  23,80,"Neppa i Issidiren, i Ineqqen. IneS afraz n yiv akked wass. Day ur tefhimem ara"
  23,81,Xaîi. Nnan akken d nnan imezwura
  23,82,"Nnan: \"Ma nemmut, nu$al d akal, d i$san, day a $ d ssekren"
  23,83,"Ni$ ippuâahed wayagi i nekwni, akw, zik, i imezwura nne$. Ayagi, siwa d timucuha imezwura"
  23,84,"Ini: \"wi p ilan tmurt, akked wayen illan degs, ma tessnem"
  23,85,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, day ur d tesmektayem ara"
  23,86,"Ini: \"anwa ay d Mass n ûa igenwan? Mass n usgeld ameqwôaêan"
  23,87,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, day ur tepêezzibem ara"
  23,88,"Ini: \"anwa i Isâan tagelda n yal cci, ger ifassen iS; Neppa Ipêarab, ur illi uêareb fellaS, ma teppissinem"
  23,89,"A d inin: \"d Öebbi\". Ini: \"ihi, acimi tepwamelkem"
  23,90,"Xaîi! Nefka yasen tidep, nitni, war ccek, d ikeddaben"
  23,91,"Ur Isâi Öebbi mmi S. Ur illi ôebbi ar tama S. Mulac yal ôebbi ad iawi ayen id ixleq, wa ad iagwar wa. Gedha s Öebbi, seg wayen id snulfuyen"
  23,92,"Amusnaw n wayen iffren akked wayen ur neffir. D Aâlayan, sennig wayen pcaraken"
  23,93,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Lemmer a yi d Tesseknev acu i sen ippuâahden"
  23,94,"A Mass iw, ur iyi Ppara deg ugdud imednas"
  23,95,"S tidep, Nezmer ad ak Nessken acu i sen Nâahed"
  23,96,"Err akin tucmip s lfayeq. Nekwni Neéôa, sennig wiyav, ayen d snulfuyen"
  23,97,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Ëerz iyi seg u$wayen n ccwaîen. Êë"
  23,98,"Ëerz iyi, a Mass iw! Ur dgi ppilin"
  23,99,"Armi, mi d tusa tmeppant yiwen degsen, inna: \"a Mass iw! Err iyi"
  23,100,"amar ad xedme$ ayen ilhan deg wayen ooi$\". Xaîi, d awal kan id inna. Tella, deffir es, tse$lit, alamma d ass n tnekra"
  23,101,"Ma ûuven di lbuq, assen, ur ppemyilin, ur pmesteqsayen"
  23,102,"Wid iwumi ééay lmizan nnsen, nitni rebêen"
  23,103,"Wid iwumi fessus lmizan nnsen, d nitni i issexsôen iman nnsen. Di Loahennama ad wekkôen"
  23,104,"A ppesser$ tmes udmawen nnsen, ad asen zelgen icenfiren"
  23,105,"Day ur awen qaren ara issekniyen iW, wanag la ten tnekôem"
  23,106,"Nnan: \"a Mass nne$! I$leb ane$ ccum nne$. Nella d agdud im$eôqen"
  23,107,"A Mass nne$! Ssuffe$ ane$ segs. Ma nesnager, ihi, d imednas ay nella"
  23,108,"Ad Yini: \"qqimet degs, ur pmeslayet"
  23,109,"Ih, illa urbaâ n imdanen iW i iqqaôen: \"a Mass nne$! Numen. Semmeê ane$, Ëun fella$, Keçç Tifev akw wid ipêunun"
  23,110,"Tettihim fellasen armi i wen sseppun asmekti W, u tdessem degsen"
  23,111,"Nek, assa, Kufa$ ten $ef wayen ûebôen. D nitni, war ccekk, ay d imerbaê"
  23,112,"Inna: \"acêal iseggwasen i teqqimem deg wakal"
  23,113,"Nnan: \"Neqqim ass, ne$ ur ibbwiv wass, steqsi wid iêepben"
  23,114,"Inna: \"cwiî kan ay teqqimen, lemmer, s tidep, day tessinem"
  23,115,"Day t$ilem Nxelq ikwen, kan, di rrayaâ; ar ur d teppu$alem $uône£"
  23,116,"Ay Meqqweô Öebbi, Agellid, Tidep! Ur illi ôebbi, siwa Neppa, Mass n usgeld ukyis"
  23,117,"Win inaâôen, ar tama n Öebbi, ôebbi nniven, ur isâi ppbut fellas, aqeîîi s ar Mass is kan. Ih, ur rebêen ara ijehliyen"
  23,118,"Ini: \"a Mass iw! Semmeê u Ëun. Keçç, Tifev akw wid ipêunun"